scenes.description: Raora, Korone, Calliope, and Kronii play a posing game called 'Say Cheese! Raora!!', attempting to fit into designated outlines on the floor.
The VTubers catch their breath after the game, discussing Kronii's surprising physical strength and competitive spirit.
The group prepares to see the final results, with Raora and Kronii playfully chanting their own names in anticipation.
Kronii is announced as the winner. Calliope explains that Raora missed her chance for a ticket due to the loss.
Korone suggests Raora do a 'cute plea' to the camera to earn a ticket despite the loss, and they set up the camera angle.
Raora performs a dramatic and cute plea, begging Korone for the ticket as the 'Raora's Cute Plea' graphics play.
Touched by the performance, Korone gives Raora a 'CLEAR' ticket. They celebrate and Raora heads off to her next game.
